T1  - Cultural Constraints on Transfer of Technology Across Nations: Implications for Research in International and Comparative Management
AU  - Kedia, Ben L.
AU  - Bhagat, Rabi S.
Y1  - 1988/10/01
PY  - 1988
DA  - 1988/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1988.4307424
