T1  - Toward Culturally Sensitive Theories of Culture Change
AU  - Wilkins, Alan L.
AU  - Dyer, W. Gibb
Y1  - 1988/10/01
PY  - 1988
DA  - 1988/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1988.4307391
